{"tid":2259661,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"林鄭月娥：下月率先安排在內地港人回港免14日檢疫","createTime":"2020-10-27T04:05:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-28T01:04:27.000Z","uid":159697,"like":2,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"0579dd5601755b3da75226f72474a50bfff2b5aa","tid":2259661,"uid":159697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T04:05:33.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥表示，當局努力爭取恢復跨境人員往來，將於下月開始率先安排在內地的香港居民免14日檢疫下回港，計劃開始時會設有配額，因現時只餘深圳灣和港珠澳大橋兩個陸路口岸運作。至於與新加坡建立航空旅遊氣泡方面，她說現時目標是在下月內實行。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥出席行政會議前又說，本港要小心「外防輸入」，目前連同比利時，一共有14個地區被列作高危地區，她今早已要求食物及衞生局，認真考慮是否將西班牙和意大利也列入高危地區，來自高危地區的人士登機前要先檢測，亦要預先訂酒店。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1556808-20201027.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1556808-20201027.htm&d=PtGeCDSqwX4ndXcvBPlETbM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=422de475\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1556808-20201027.htm&h=1fc11005\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1556808-20201027.htm</a>"},{"pid":"45b6c138e0f272aed2b675966be2834d2a740b41","tid":2259661,"uid":48277,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T04:06:10.000Z","msg":"第4波黎了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a11fafed197617ce6c18bbc9946f0cbf53e56408","tid":2259661,"uid":159697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T04:06:39.000Z","msg":"播毒師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0830dc61a493ecde3fae9357aabc6244fdc8ec04","tid":2259661,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T04:07:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\